== Overview ==
An EM Wave Emitter generate a constant stream of magnetic resonance waves almost completely dispersing any incoming energy drain effects.

== Where to Acquire ==
The EM Wave Emitter can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in [[Vulcore]].
